Yarrie mine, Western Australia


Brazil

Samarco: a joint-venture with Vale S.A. (50% ownership each). It is responsible for the worst environmental disaster in the history of mining in Brazil:[64] the collapse of two iron ore tailings dams[65] in Bento Rodrigues, a subdistrict of Mariana.


Canada

Jansen potash development project, Saskatchewan


Chile

Escondida
